{"tid":415822,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺火影選舉好小圈子？","createTime":"2017-09-27T09:50:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-28T07:14:50.000Z","uid":5455,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"27d948c69d21251fffa5d5ea0e918b5be691894c","tid":415822,"uid":5455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T09:50:49.000Z","msg":"初代傳位比佢自己細佬二代<br />\n<br />\n二代之後又到佢自己個徒弟做三代<br />\n<br />\n四代係自來也徒弟，而自來也=三代徒弟<br />\n<br />\n到第五代，不但止又係三代既徒弟，仲係初代個孫女<br />\n<br />\n第六代就係四代徒弟<br />\n<br />\n第七代就係六代徒弟<br />\n<br />\n總結就係你地自己圍內玩哂佢得啦，木葉咁多大家族得宇智波一族夠膽出聲反抗，可惜就比人用計減族，果班權貴related party就千秋萬世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好寫實"},{"pid":"414b5c5287e6612039321d616a6a5c9e839d448e","tid":415822,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T09:53:35.000Z","msg":"事實上就係做火影果班關係者最好揪"},{"pid":"54b31b66408ce1e4cf5d8aae56ece3af6d53e077","tid":415822,"uid":37735,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T09:55:08.000Z","msg":"講起又係<br />\n<br />\n如果講關係繼承仲衰過中共 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb06ff25bf3224b5b0f8ba7c538db70f292c27b6","tid":415822,"uid":73728,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T09:59:15.000Z","msg":"岩呀 班火影根本壟斷政治 又利用鼬 支持宇智波反佢地班偽君子"},{"pid":"ee6e7c959fc197b047dbacd3b0943b56f5c78cb1","tid":415822,"uid":5455,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T10:01:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>事實上就係做火影果班關係者最好揪</blockquote><br />\n人地宇智波幾部高達呀，有冇邊個做到火影？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46f9dbb1383ebaa6d955f230ddf403ce5bd620cd","tid":415822,"uid":34293,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T10:04:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>事實上就係做火影果班關係者最好揪</blockquote><br />\n人地宇智波幾部高達呀，有冇邊個做到火影？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n得班係智力正常  高出他人水平<br />\n你搵其他D弱智做火影?"},{"